# leeway

> Leeway is a heavily caching build system for Go, Yarn and Docker projects.
> More information: <https://github.com/gitpod-io/leeway>.

- List resources within a workspace:

`leeway collect {{components|packages|scripts|files}}`

- Show a tree of dependencies for a given package/component:

`leeway describe tree {{path/to/dir:package}}`

- Build a package:

`leeway build {{path/to/dir:package}}`

- Describe a script:

`leeway describe script {{path/to/dir:script}}`

- Run a specific script:

`leeway run {{path/to/dir:script}} [-D BUILDARG=arg]`